{/* Vision and Mission Section */}
Welcome to sensAIra

AI-powered wearable for proactive health monitoring

{/* Problem and Solution Section */}

Our Vision and Mission

Vision: To improve the quality of life for people.

Mission: We aim to use AI and remote monitoring technologies to provide personalized healthcare for the elderly, ensuring early warnings, continuous monitoring, and making healthcare accessible and effective.

Problem Statement

The world's aging population is growing rapidly, but healthcare services are often inaccessible, costly, or inefficient for the elderly. 70% of seniors have at least one chronic condition, and 40% have two or more.

Health Stats

  • 41.9% of adults aged 45 and over are hypertensive.
  • 9.5% of total deaths in India are caused by COPD.
  • 55 million patients of COPD in India.
